subject: architecture property metadef should include valid enums

values.-1: This patch needs further work before it can be merged
values.+1: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve

messages.message:
Patch Set 1: Workflow-1

This updates the architecture property, but the other properties in this namespace don't seem to want to update from properties.  Need to figure out why.  May end up moving architecture in the hypervisor namespace with hypervisor_type and vm_mode.
